1. *Hleb* je osnovna namirnica u našoj ishrani. (Bread is a staple food in our diet.)
2. Ne volim kad mi *hleb* bude suv. (I don't like it when my bread is dry.)
3. Za doručak sam pojeo *hleba* i marmeladu. (For breakfast, I ate bread and jam.)
4. *Hlebom* sam nahranio goluba. (I fed the pigeon with bread.)
5. Pečem *hleb* u svom novom rerni. (I'm baking bread in my new oven.)
6. Daj mi *hleb* s desne strane. (Give me the bread on the right side.)
7. Naša pekara pravi najbolji *hleb* u gradu. (Our bakery makes the best bread in town.)
8. Moram da kupim novu kesu *hleba*. (I need to buy a new bag of bread.)
9. *Hleb* je bio tako ukusan da sam pojeo celu veknu. (The bread was so delicious that I ate the whole loaf.)
10. Ukoliko imate viška *hleba*, možete ga dati u humanitarne svrhe. (If you have leftover bread, you can donate it for humanitarian purposes.)